    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/5bd2a788134dfd964f893b70fe66ad15.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/5bd2a788134dfd964f893b70fe66ad15.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=2366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Agni: Village of Calamity </strong>is a cinematic survival horror game inspired by the greatest classics of horror media. <strong>Play as Agni</strong>, a determined investigator from a covert Indonesian police unit who defied orders and ventures into a remote village despite ominous warnings. What begins as an unauthorized investigation quickly plunges Agni into a horrifying reality that shatters her understanding of everything she knows. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Explore the eerie village, uncover its dark secrets, and confront terrifying horrors as you go deeper into the nexus of the mystery. Navigate through a cold atmosphere, solve puzzles, and survive against relentless threats. </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/6a2ec150d9778197a6eb7089613e67a4.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/6a2ec150d9778197a6eb7089613e67a4.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/e997ee6d253d08a75d20cd182f3a418d.poster.avif?t=1770029715\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/e997ee6d253d08a75d20cd182f3a418d.webm?t=1770029715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/e997ee6d253d08a75d20cd182f3a418d.mp4?t=1770029715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/9cc53225fe1248f76821464bc5dda995.avif?t=1770029715\" width=1560 height=1808 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive the Darkness</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a perilous journey through a village shrouded in dread where survival is of utmost importance. Collect essential items and manage your resources wisely. Face intense combat situations where you'll need to decide between confrontation and evasion. The horrors lurking within the village will test your resolve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/c809fd27112392f39e5c3ad69149a48a.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/c809fd27112392f39e5c3ad69149a48a.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/a9e2d4ccc72650247b35f4806c6c13e7.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/a9e2d4ccc72650247b35f4806c6c13e7.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/55a562e9258486636260cfffa6f3d879.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/55a562e9258486636260cfffa6f3d879.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=652 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Investigate and Explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate the mysteries of Desa Purba, gathering clues that lead through a maze of deception and revelation. Explore the cold, oppressive environment, solve the puzzles, and confront dangers that lurks in every corner. Each discovery brings you closer to unraveling the village's dark secrets and finding Agni’s missing partner</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/8714cfebbf69b5f76dbbc0758c4bf277.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/8714cfebbf69b5f76dbbc0758c4bf277.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/e9cb3708ac7d7381fe99738fde9a63c6.poster.avif?t=1770029715\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/e9cb3708ac7d7381fe99738fde9a63c6.webm?t=1770029715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/e9cb3708ac7d7381fe99738fde9a63c6.mp4?t=1770029715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/fca46786321bbd0779847428c85c692a.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/fca46786321bbd0779847428c85c692a.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unravel the Mystery</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collecting clues is only the beginning. Agni must piece together the clues based on information gathered from around the village to unlock the answers to each conundrum. Progress through the narrative and deepen Agni’s understanding of Desa Purba's mysteries and the fate of Lila. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/1ac5dd90437dae1df4ad0110018e0364.poster.avif?t=1770029715\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/1ac5dd90437dae1df4ad0110018e0364.webm?t=1770029715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/1ac5dd90437dae1df4ad0110018e0364.mp4?t=1770029715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/c4e6b43a254c8c7254f4a21faa1bdcee.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/c4e6b43a254c8c7254f4a21faa1bdcee.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/a6edb302d9b25a90d1a22f3208a13454.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/a6edb302d9b25a90d1a22f3208a13454.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/e6f55424721003cea65e3937eaa90a6d.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/e6f55424721003cea65e3937eaa90a6d.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face Inner Demons </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the journey, Agni grapples with guilt, fear of abandonment, and unresolved trauma from her past. Her perilous journey tests her resolve as she confronts her inner demons while striving to find out what happened and find her missing partner.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/a7e3be0d6967aec06b5d6b7be573d81d.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/a7e3be0d6967aec06b5d6b7be573d81d.avif?t=1770029715 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/485fad605b21bc2aaea5a316a3cf5b7c.avif?t=1770029715\" width=1560 height=804 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Haunting Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/8e791ed44bb9142ec3575fdad9bb5669.poster.avif?t=1770029715\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/8e791ed44bb9142ec3575fdad9bb5669.webm?t=1770029715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/8e791ed44bb9142ec3575fdad9bb5669.mp4?t=1770029715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafted with a deep love for horror media, AGNI: Village of Calamity combines modern graphics, a cinematic presentation, and a fixed camera perspective reminiscent of the greatest classics of the genre.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras/b73f56c4e7587db91e5fccc8d46cc12c.avif?t=1770029715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151360/extras_big/b73f56c4e7587db91e5fccc8d46cc12c.avif?t=1770029715 width=1560 height=850 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Prepare for a journey into darkness. Will Agni discover the harrowing truth and find Lila, or will the village’s malevolent secrets devour both of them, leaving them lost into the abyss for eternity?</i></p>",
